root: ^If I eat fairy dust, am I gonna be able to make a wish and get out of here?
^I don't know. It just seems like this is one of the least cursed things to put in my drink. Let's just try it.
^Uh. I'm still here. The only difference is this magical scroll appeared in front of me.
^It says... "You have consumed fairy dust. Haha, you're stuck here forever now!"
